# 5. Unit Testing

## Purpose

Unit Testing validates individual components.

It ensures each module works correctly in isolation.

Examples:

- Functions
- Classes
- Services
- APIs
- Components

---

## Unit Testing Scope

Includes:

- Input validation
- Output correctness
- Error handling
- Internal logic

---

## Unit Testing Flow

Developer

↓

Write Test

↓

Execute Test

↓

Analyze Result

↓

Improve Code

---

# 6. Integration Testing

## Purpose

Integration Testing validates communication between components.

It ensures different cmdOS modules work together correctly.

Examples:

- Agent and Capability communication
- Runtime and Kernel communication
- Plugin and SDK interaction

---

## Integration Testing Scope

Includes:

- API communication
- Data exchange
- Message handling
- Workflow execution

---

